OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Candidates to be the UK's next prime   
OL,6, minister should focus on growth and an 
OL,7, overhaul of the tax system over quick  
OL,8, cuts, a business group has said.       
OL,10,FPromises of tax reductions feature     
OL,11,Fheavily in the leadership campaigns but
OL,12,Fthe CBI business group said the wrong  
OL,13,Fcuts could fuel inflation further.     
OL,15,FIn an open letter, CBI director general
OL,16,FTony Danker called for "serious,       
OL,17,Fcredible and bold plans for growth".   
OL,19,FLabour's Rachel Reeves said candidates 
OL,20,Fshould "seriously heed these warnings".
